data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning three-bedroom, two-bath residence is a true gem nestled conveniently close to the highway for easy commuting, yet offering a tranquil escape with serene water vistas. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a beautifully decorated interior, where modern aesthetics meet cozy comfort. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the spacious living area to a comfortable kitchen, perfect for both entertaining and day-to-day living. Beyond the stunning interior, this home is located in a fantastic community that's known for its friendly atmosphere and giant oak tree entrance. Whether it's relaxing on your back porch, taking in the view, or enjoying the beautiful split plan home this property truly offers the best of both worlds. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to make this house your forever home. Contact me today to schedule a viewing and experience the perfect blend of convenience, luxury, and community living.
